				<div class="desc-half-list">
					<p>Without extensive system analytical knowledge or heavy support from IT,
					within 3 months SEO Department head Tomas Vyskocil was able to
					change the daily operations of the company. He lead his team towards integrating,
					cleaning and transforming all data sources into usable dashboards.
					These dashboards are now in used every day across the organization and serve
					as the basis for </p>
					<p>
					making fast and appropriate decisions.
						Due to his actions, this system has received widespread support,
						won many internal advocates, and is spreading from internal use towards
						client facing applications.</p>
				</div>
			</div></article>

			<article class="article">
